{"tid":2224671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【#商業熱話】中國準備對Google發起反壟斷調查","createTime":"2020-09-30T16:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T16:23:07.000Z","uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1c242a39fc1b00a522acf969ddab6eb6810c07","tid":2224671,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"據《路透》引述消息，中國準備對Google發起反壟斷調查，調查Google利用Android系統優勢妨礙競爭。據悉，是次調查案由華為提議，中國反壟斷監管機構已提交國務院審核。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，中國還將調查Google的市場地位，是否可能對華為等中企造成「極端損害」的指控。美國之前將華為列入貿易黑名單，導致華為手機無法使用Google應用程式及服務。華為亦以操作系統鴻蒙，應對美國封殺。<br />\n<br />\n據報，對於是否要展開正式調查，最快可能10月決定，而有關決定或受到中美關係影響。另外，中國據報正著手大修改反壟斷法，擬議中的調整包括大幅提高罰款上限，並擴大判斷一間企業操控市場的標準範圍。<br />\n<br />\n消息來源：Reuters<br />\n製圖／編輯：Business Digest<br />\n網站文章：<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/article/business/5064/huawei/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2F5064%2Fhuawei%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kymmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=965b8807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/article/business/5064/huawei/</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【搶先看，讓你更緊貼商業世界】：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/BusinessDigest.io/follow_menu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FBusinessDigest.io%2Ffollow_menu%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kymmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=f12c2166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/BusinessDigest.io/follow_menu/</a><br />\n<br />\n【立即追蹤Instagram，緊貼獨家IG Story】：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/business.digest.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbusiness.digest.io%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kymmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=d0726ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/business.digest.io/</a>"},{"pid":"3413df5a976e11c52d47b3340b89dbbed7e1e4fc","tid":2224671,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s